This '''[[Template:Convert/LoffAonSoff]]''' invokes [[Template:Convert/outsep]] to display the converted result and unit symbol (if any), with {sep} to control wrapping. A number < 1,000 is not wrapped, or if the unit symbol is used, then only numbers above 20,000 can wrap at the unit symbol. If the unit symbol {{{u}}} is not set (such as with "acre"), then it passes both the singular unit name {{{n}}} and plural, {{{l}}}, or "{{{n}}}s" when no specific plural name has been defined.

